name: Analog Fabric – Signal Culture Study 01
description: These video studies (720x480, no audio) were created at the Signal Culture Residency Program in Owego, NY in the spring of 2015. Working with an LZX Video Synth, Wobbulator, Dave Jones Vector Rescanner, Hearn Videolab, and related analog video studio tools were captured from CRT monitor and Oscilloscope via camera.
